---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Conditions We Treat" description="The Bridge Chiropractic treats back pain, neck pain, sciatica, headaches, balance issues, and more. Dr. Nathan Beyerl offers personalized care for adults 55+ in San Diego.">
  <!-- Page Hero -->
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="section__eyebrow">Comprehensive Care</span>
      <h1>Conditions We Treat</h1>
      <p>Personalized treatment for a wide range of musculoskeletal and neurological conditions.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Intro -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="intro-card" data-animate="fade-up">
        <div class="intro-card__icon">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M20.84 4.61a5.5 5.5 0 0 0-7.78 0L12 5.67l-1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 0 0-7.78 7.78l1.06 1.06L12 21.23l7.78-7.78 1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 0 0 0-7.78z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <p>Every patient who walks through our doors receives individualized care. What works for one person may not work for another—that's why Dr. Beyerl takes time to understand YOUR specific condition, goals, and concerns before creating a treatment plan.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Spinal Conditions -->
  <section class="section section--alt">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header-row" data-animate="fade-up">
        <div class="section-header-content">
          <span class="section__eyebrow">Spinal Health</span>
          <h2>Back & Neck Conditions</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="section-header-icon">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M12 2v20M9 5h6M9 9h6M9 13h6M9 17h6M7 21h10"/></svg>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="conditions-grid stagger-children">
        <div class="condition-card">
          <div class="condition-card__number">01</div>
          <h3>Low Back Pain</h3>
          <p>Whether from injury, poor posture, or degenerative changes, we address the root cause of your low back pain through adjustments, soft tissue work, and movement training.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="condition-card">
          <div class="condition-card__number">02</div>
          <h3>Neck Pain & Stiffness</h3>
          <p>Office work, phone use, and daily stress can create chronic neck tension. We restore mobility and reduce pain through gentle, targeted care.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="condition-card">
          <div class="condition-card__number">03</div>
          <h3>Sciatica</h3>
          <p>Radiating leg pain from sciatic nerve compression responds well to chiropractic care that addresses both the spine and surrounding soft tissues.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="condition-card">
          <div class="condition-card__number">04</div>
          <h3>Herniated Discs</h3>
          <p>Disc issues require careful, individualized treatment. We use gentle techniques to reduce pressure and promote healing without aggressive intervention.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="condition-card">
          <div class="condition-card__number">05</div>
          <h3>Degenerative Disc Disease</h3>
          <p>Age-related spinal changes don't have to mean living with pain. We help maintain mobility and manage symptoms for long-term quality of life.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="condition-card">
          <div class="condition-card__number">06</div>
          <h3>Spinal Stenosis</h3>
          <p>Narrowing of the spinal canal can cause pain and mobility issues. Our conservative approach helps manage symptoms and maintain function.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Joint & Musculoskeletal -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header-row" data-animate="fade-up">
        <div class="section-header-content">
          <span class="section__eyebrow">Joint Health</span>
          <h2>Joint & Musculoskeletal Issues</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="section-header-icon">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3"/><path d="M12 2v4M12 18v4M2 12h4M18 12h4M4.93 4.93l2.83 2.83M16.24 16.24l2.83 2.83M4.93 19.07l2.83-2.83M16.24 7.76l2.83-2.83"/></svg>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="conditions-grid stagger-children">
        <div class="condition-card">
          <div class="condition-card__number">01</div>
          <h3>Shoulder Pain</h3>
          <p>From rotator cuff issues to frozen shoulder, we address the mechanics of shoulder dysfunction to restore pain-free movement.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="condition-card">
          <div class="condition-card__number">02</div>
          <h3>Hip Pain</h3>
          <p>Hip problems affect walking, sitting, and overall quality of life. We evaluate the entire kinetic chain to address the source of your discomfort.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="condition-card">
          <div class="condition-card__number">03</div>
          <h3>Knee Pain</h3>
          <p>Knee issues often relate to hip, ankle, or spinal alignment. Our whole-body approach addresses contributing factors, not just symptoms.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="condition-card">
          <div class="condition-card__number">04</div>
          <h3>Arthritis</h3>
          <p>While we can't reverse arthritis, we can significantly improve comfort and function through gentle mobilization and targeted exercise.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="condition-card">
          <div class="condition-card__number">05</div>
          <h3>Muscle Strains & Sprains</h3>
          <p>Soft tissue injuries benefit from proper treatment to ensure complete healing and prevent chronic issues from developing.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="condition-card">
          <div class="condition-card__number">06</div>
          <h3>Postural Problems</h3>
          <p>Poor posture creates pain patterns throughout the body. We address both the structural and habitual components of postural dysfunction.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Head & Neurological -->
  <section class="section section--alt">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header-row" data-animate="fade-up">
        <div class="section-header-content">
          <span class="section__eyebrow">Neurological Care</span>
          <h2>Head & Neurological Conditions</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="section-header-icon">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M12 16v-4M12 8h.01"/></svg>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="conditions-grid conditions-grid--4 stagger-children">
        <div class="condition-card">
          <div class="condition-card__number">01</div>
          <h3>Headaches</h3>
          <p>Many headaches originate from neck tension and spinal dysfunction. Chiropractic care can provide lasting relief without medication.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="condition-card">
          <div class="condition-card__number">02</div>
          <h3>Migraines</h3>
          <p>While migraines have many triggers, spinal care can reduce frequency and intensity for many sufferers.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="condition-card">
          <div class="condition-card__number">03</div>
          <h3>Dizziness & Vertigo</h3>
          <p>Balance disturbances often respond to specialized vestibular rehabilitation and gentle cervical care.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="condition-card">
          <div class="condition-card__number">04</div>
          <h3>TMJ Disorders</h3>
          <p>Jaw pain and dysfunction often connect to neck and postural issues. We address the underlying mechanics contributing to TMJ problems.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Senior-Specific -->
  <section class="section section--highlight">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="highlight-header" data-animate="fade-up">
        <div class="highlight-badge">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M12 2L2 7l10 5 10-5-10-5z"/><path d="M2 17l10 5 10-5"/><path d="M2 12l10 5 10-5"/></svg>
          Specialty Program
        </div>
        <h2>Specialized Care for Adults 55+</h2>
        <p>Our neuro rehabilitation program specifically addresses age-related concerns with proven techniques.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="highlight-grid stagger-children">
        <div class="highlight-card">
          <div class="highlight-card__icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Fall Risk & Prevention</h3>
          <p>Our brain/neuro rehabilitation program is specifically designed to reduce fall risk in older adults through balance training and coordination exercises.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="highlight-card">
          <div class="highlight-card__icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M8 12h8M12 8v8"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Balance Disorders</h3>
          <p>Age-related balance changes don't have to limit your independence. We help retrain your brain-body connection for improved stability.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="highlight-card">
          <div class="highlight-card__icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M13 2L3 14h9l-1 8 10-12h-9l1-8z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Gait Problems</h3>
          <p>Changes in walking patterns can increase fall risk and reduce mobility. We analyze and address the factors affecting your gait.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="highlight-card">
          <div class="highlight-card__icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Coordination Issues</h3>
          <p>Decreased coordination affects daily activities. Our neuro rehab program helps improve motor control and confidence.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Important Note -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="note-box" data-animate="scale">
        <div class="note-box__icon">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M21 15a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H7l-4 4V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h14a2 2 0 0 1 2 2z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h2>A Note on Our Approach</h2>
        <p>Patients often tell us "I didn't know you treated that!" That's because what one patient needs might be completely different from another. We don't follow cookie-cutter treatment protocols—we listen, assess, and create a plan specific to YOU.</p>
        <p>If you're unsure whether chiropractic care can help your condition, please reach out. We're happy to have a conversation about your specific situation and whether our approach might be right for you.</p>
        <a href="/contact" class="btn btn--primary">Ask Us About Your Condition</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="cta-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="cta-content" data-animate="fade-up">
        <h2>Ready to Address Your Condition?</h2>
        <p>Schedule your consultation and let's discuss how we can help you move better and feel better.</p>
        <div class="cta-actions">
          <a href="/contact" class="btn btn--white btn--lg">Book Your Consultation</a>
          <a href="tel:8582777500" class="btn btn--outline-white btn--lg">Call (858) 277-7500</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  /* Page Hero */
  .page-hero {
    background: var(--color-off-white);
    padding: 160px 0 80px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .page-hero h1 {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .page-hero p {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--color-gray-dark);
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  /* Intro Card */
  .intro-card {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: var(--space-xl);
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: var(--space-2xl);
    background: var(--color-white);
    border: 2px solid var(--color-primary);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
  }

  .intro-card__icon {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 64px;
    height: 64px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    background: var(--color-primary);
    border-radius: 50%;
    color: var(--color-white);
  }

  .intro-card p {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--color-charcoal);
  }

  /* Section Alt */
  .section--alt {
    background: var(--color-off-white);
  }

  /* Section Header Row */
  .section-header-row {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-3xl);
    padding-bottom: var(--space-xl);
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--color-gray-light);
  }

  .section-header-content h2 {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .section-header-icon {
    width: 80px;
    height: 80px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    background: var(--color-primary-light);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    color: var(--color-primary);
  }

  /* Conditions Grid */
  .conditions-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .conditions-grid--4 {
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
  }

  /* Condition Card */
  .condition-card {
    position: relative;
    background: var(--color-white);
    padding: var(--space-xl);
    padding-top: var(--space-2xl);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-gray-light);
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .condition-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--color-primary);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
    transform: translateY(-4px);
  }

  .condition-card__number {
    position: absolute;
    top: var(--space-md);
    right: var(--space-md);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    background: var(--color-primary-light);
    padding: 4px 10px;
    border-radius: 20px;
  }

  .condition-card h3 {
    color: var(--color-charcoal);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
    font-size: 1.125rem;
  }

  .condition-card p {
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--color-gray-dark);
    line-height: 1.7;
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
  }

  /* Highlight Section */
  .section--highlight {
    background: var(--color-primary);
    padding: var(--space-4xl) 0;
  }

  .highlight-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-3xl);
  }

  .highlight-badge {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-sm);
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
    color: var(--color-white);
    padding: var(--space-sm) var(--space-lg);
    border-radius: 30px;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .highlight-header h2 {
    color: var(--color-white);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .highlight-header p {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .highlight-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .highlight-card {
    background: var(--color-white);
    padding: var(--space-xl);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--space-lg);
    align-items: flex-start;
  }

  .highlight-card__icon {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 56px;
    height: 56px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    background: var(--color-primary-light);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    color: var(--color-primary);
  }

  .highlight-card h3 {
    color: var(--color-charcoal);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xs);
    font-size: 1.125rem;
  }

  .highlight-card p {
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--color-gray-dark);
    line-height: 1.7;
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
  }

  /* Note Box */
  .note-box {
    background: var(--color-off-white);
    padding: var(--space-3xl);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    border-left: 4px solid var(--color-primary);
  }

  .note-box__icon {
    width: 64px;
    height: 64px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    background: var(--color-white);
    border-radius: 50%;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    margin: 0 auto var(--space-lg);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
  }

  .note-box h2 {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .note-box p {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  /* CTA Section */
  .cta-section {
    background: var(--color-primary);
    padding: var(--space-4xl) 0;
  }

  .cta-content {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .cta-content h2 {
    color: var(--color-white);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .cta-content p {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .cta-actions {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--space-md);
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  /* Button Variants */
  .btn--white {
    background: var(--color-white);
    color: var(--color-charcoal);
  }

  .btn--white:hover {
    background: var(--color-off-white);
  }

  .btn--outline-white {
    background: transparent;
    color: var(--color-white);
    border: 2px solid var(--color-white);
  }

  .btn--outline-white:hover {
    background: var(--color-white);
    color: var(--color-charcoal);
  }

  /* Responsive */
  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .conditions-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }

    .section-header-icon {
      display: none;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .page-hero {
      padding: 130px 0 60px;
    }

    .intro-card {
      flex-direction: column;
      text-align: center;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .conditions-grid,
    .conditions-grid--4,
    .highlight-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .highlight-card {
      flex-direction: column;
      text-align: center;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .section-header-row {
      text-align: center;
      justify-content: center;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .page-hero {
      padding: 110px 0 40px;
    }

    .intro-card {
      padding: var(--space-xl);
    }

    .condition-card {
      padding: var(--space-lg);
      padding-top: var(--space-xl);
    }

    .highlight-card {
      padding: var(--space-lg);
    }

    .note-box {
      padding: var(--space-xl);
    }

    .cta-actions {
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    .cta-actions .btn {
      width: 100%;
    }
  }
</style>
